{
  "texts": [
    "We conclude that the backtranslated instructions are generally faithful to the original text.",
    "Instructions in Suri focus primarily on long-form text generation, particularly crafting narratives or articles.",
    "Therefore, the key element that introduces diversity across these instructions is the accompanying list of constraints.",
    "Here, we measure the proportion of constraints being broad/specific or focusing on semantic/stylistic elements.",
    "We prompt Mistral-7B-Instruct-v0.2 (Jiang et al., 2023), 8 to assign each constraint to the applicable category."
  ]
}